        <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2018/09/29/opinion/sunday/in-praise-of-mediocrity.html&quot;&gt;In Praise of Mediocrity - The New York Times&lt;/a&gt; →&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Tim Wu on having hobbies:&lt;/p&gt;

