      <item>
      	
        <description>&lt;p&gt;A few weeks ago I asked if anyone ever &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.endonend.org/2018/09/21/has-anyone-ever.html&quot;&gt;deleted their entire Apple Music collection and started over&lt;/a&gt;. Well, I just did. Re-booting and adding back with purpose and mindful of the all-you-can-eat world we live in now. Before: 44,000+ songs. Current: 1,486 and a focus on quality.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
